{"story":{"group_1":[{"bg":"bg_adv_21027.jpg","bgm":"bgm03_story09","chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403401,"motion":1,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403201,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"Chisato","nameRight":"Arisa","textLeft":"So I decided to take parts from each of@our ideas...","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":403401}],"textLeft":"...and turn them into one complete story."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":403401,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"This is what I came up with!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403301,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"textRight":"Okay, let's hear it!"},{"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":403401},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403301,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameNarration":"Chisato","narration":"First, there are four protagonists.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"They are all girls who@live in separate villages."},{"chara":[{"id":403301}],"nameCenter":"Arisa","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"Four girls?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403201,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameNarration":"Chisato","narration":"In this world, there's an evil@demon king who torments people.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"One day, the spirit of a white rabbit@appears in front of these four girls@and gives them magical powers -@the power to defeat the demon king."},{"chara":[{"id":403201,"motion":100}],"nameCenter":"Matsuri","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"Oh! There's a rabbit in the story!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403501,"motion":1,"pos":1}],"nameNarration":"Chisato","narration":"But in order to unleash their true power,@the girls need to come together.@So the four of them have to travel across all@kinds of countries to unite with each other.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"id":403501}],"nameCenter":"Haruka","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"Countries... Like Caldesheim? And Conshawl?"},{"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":403501},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403301,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403401,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameNarration":"Chisato","narration":"After many difficulties, the four gather@together and combine their strength.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"id":403401}],"nameLeft":"Chisato","nameRight":"Arisa","narrationEffect":"out","textLeft":"...And finally defeat the demon king. A@happily ever after ending. What do you think?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403401}],"textLeft":"I don't have the details worked out yet, but@that's the gist of it."},{"chara":[{"id":403301}],"textRight":"Hmm."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403301,"motion":100}],"textRight":"I think it's fine. Like, it has a story that@makes sense and everything!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403201,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Matsuri","textRight":"Yeah! And the rabbit is an important@character!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403501,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Haruka","textRight":"I agree! We have the perfect base now!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403401,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"You really think so? I'm so glad."},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403501,"motion":200}],"textRight":"But..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403401,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"But?"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story16","chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403501}],"textRight":"Can we name the rabbit spirit \"Stéphan\"?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403201,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Matsuri","textRight":"The rabbit should be \"Little Rabbit\"!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403301,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Arisa","textRight":"Their magic power though, it's gotta be,@like, a ball of light that goes BOOM!"},{"chara":[{"id":403401,"motion":400}],"textLeft":"Huh? What?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403501,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Haruka","textRight":"\"Sylvère\" or \"Matthias\" would work as well."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403201,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Matsuri","textRight":"Let's add a raccoon and a fox too!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403301,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Arisa","textRight":"What about magical missiles?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403401,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":403401,"lipSynch":0}],"textLeft":"(This is going to take a while.)"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}